<br>
At Dylan's request, the crew had toned down their teasing a <br>
bit.  It didn't totally stop.  Beka was kind of getting used to the 'How's Granny?' remarks.  Even from Tyr.  She sethed inside but was no longer openly hostile.  There was no point.  <br>
